  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Principal Data Scientist (Aerospace)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Lead and collaborate with data scientists and analysts to drive innovation, knowledge sharing, and continuous improvement.</li><li>Design, develop, and deploy robust analytical and machine learning models using advanced statistical techniques.</li><li>Partner with business and technical stakeholders to identify key challenges and translate them into data-driven solutions.</li><li>Develop dashboards and data visualisations to effectively communicate insights to technical and non-technical audiences.</li><li>Stay current with emerging data science trends, tools, and methodologies, applying relevant advancements where appropriate.</li><li>Contribute to the establishment and enhancement of data governance, data quality, and analytics best practices.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Master’s degree or PhD in Data Science, Statistics, Machine Learning, Computer Science, or a related quantitative discipline.</li><li>Significant hands-on experience in data science or advanced analytics roles, preferably within complex engineering or operational environments.</li><li>Strong proficiency in Python and/or SQL, with experience using machine learning libraries and frameworks.</li><li>Demonstrated ability to manage multiple projects concurrently and deliver high-quality outcomes in a fast-paced setting.</li><li>Strong analytical and problem-solving skills, with the ability to interpret and extract insights from complex datasets.</li><li>Excellent communication and stakeholder engagement skills, with the ability to explain technical concepts clearly to non-technical audiences.</li><li>Familiarity with enterprise systems (e.g. PLM, MES, MRO) and cloud platforms such as AWS will be advantageous.</li></ul><p>To submit your application, please apply online to <a href=\"mailto:apply@rn-care.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>apply@rn-care.com </strong></a>or call <strong>+(65) </strong><a href=\"tel:6513 5697\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>6513 5697</strong></a> for private and confidential discussion.</p><p>Your interest will be treated with the strictest of confidence. We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified or contacted.</p><p><strong>RN Care Pte. Ltd</strong><br /><strong>EA License No: 17C8900</strong></p>",
